@NODE HISTORY "Program History"

@{B}@{I}VERSION HISTORY @{UB}@{UI}

@{I}v1.42 (23 May 98) - LAST EVER VERSION @{UI}
· Included Blitz Basic source code

@{I}v1.41 (18 May 98) @{UI}
· When the timer reached over 100 hours, now it won't do strange
  things to the prefs file
· Executable file now compressed

@{I}v1.40 (09 Apr 98) @{UI}
· Small cosmetic changes to the Prefs GUI and the screen and window
  titlebars
· Fixed a small bug with using the FRACTION parameter from the Shell
· Added the Autosave Prefs feature
· Added a simple alarm/remind feature

@{I}v1.32 (19 Feb 98) @{UI}
· Added an About window rather than having my name in the screen's
  titlebar
· Windows on systems set to use large fonts appear properly now

@{I}v1.31 (15 Feb 98) @{UI}
· Prefs file can be saved into any existing directory
· Running ITimer for a second time will close the program
· Using "RESET" Tooltype/CLI parameter will work now
· Decided to not include the Installer script: Simply unarchive
  the file into the desired directory
· New archive naming for making spotting updates on Aminet easier
  (eg ITimer1_31.lha)

@{I}v1.30 (06 Feb 98) @{UI}
· Now includes an Installer script for easier installing/updating
· Can now calculate online charges
· Snapshot window position in prefs file
· Extra commands added to CLI interface
· Can now use Tooltypes to activate CLI options from Workbench
· Inserted a OS-readable version string into the code

@{I}v1.21 (11 Jan 98) - Not Released @{UI}
· Now two reset buttons
· At last! I now have a decent icon for ITimer! I have one from the
  Magic Workbench distribution that I have decided to use. I've also
  used MWB icons for the docs
· New filename for archive (ITimer.lha as opposed to i-timer.lha)

@{I}v1.20 (29 Dec 97) @{UI}
· The timer is now much more accurate on those systems which previously
  had difficulty in timekeeping

@{I}v1.11 (29 Nov 97) @{UI}
· Acknowledgements page in this guide works now!
· I didn't like my icon, so I'll use the default Blitz one. Can anyone
  draw me a good one?
· Now ITimer won't crash if you try to place the window out of the screen

@{I}v1.10 (18 Nov 97) @{UI}
· Added a CLI interface to control the startup of ITimer
· Redesigned (sort of) this page of the Guide file
· Designed my own ITimer icon

@{I}v1.04 (01 Nov 97) @{UI}
· Smaller, less obtrusive window.
· Changed the help doc to AmigaGuide format to make it easier to
  read and update.

@{I}v1.03 (23 Oct 97) - Not Released on Aminet @{UI}
· Internal programming changes only to make final executable file
  smaller.

@{I}v1.02 (22 Oct 97) @{UI}
· Now ITimer will not use all of the CPU time.

@{I}v1.01 (21 Oct 97) @{UI}
· Now ITimer doesn't crash when you quit it.

@{I}v1.00 (20 Oct 97) @{UI}
