@ENDNODE

@NODE FUTURE "Future Development"

@{B}@{I}FUTURE DEVELOPMENT @{UB}@{UI}

*** IMPORTANT!!!!!!! ***
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

NO MORE DEVELOPMENT WILL BE DONE ON ITIMER AS (DUE TO EDUCATIONAL
REQUIREMENTS) MY AMIGA IS BEING REPLACED BY A PC. I KNOW THERE ARE
AMIGA EMULATORS, BUT I HAVE TO SELL MY ENTIRE AMIGA SETUP PLUS
ALL THE SOFTWARE TO FINANCE THE CHANGE.

IF ANYONE CONTACTS ME SAYING "ITIMER DOESN'T WORK BECAUSE OF
SO-AND-SO" ALL YOU'LL GET IS A REPLY SAYING SOMETHING ABOUT
THE BLITZ BASIC SOURCE CODE BEING INCLUDED WITH ITIMER.
ITIMER IS NOW OFFICIALLY UNSUPPORTED AS OF THIS RELEASE.

I honestly hate having to dump everyone like this, but as good as
Amiga's are, they still can't run MS Office which is why I'm getting
it (I use it at college, and next year I'm doing an HND course).

It's been a fun four years owning my Amiga, but sadly the time has
come for me to say goodbye and move on (sniff, sob).

@ENDNODE

